    {
        "content": "<p>This works:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Std</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span> <span class=\"n\">Lean</span> <span class=\"n\">Elab</span> <span class=\"n\">Tactic</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">elab</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"add_true\"</span> <span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"n\">ident</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">tactic</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"k\">do</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">evalTactic</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">‚Üê</span> <span class=\"bp\">`</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">tactic</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"k\">have</span> <span class=\"bp\">$</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"n\">ident</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">True</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"n\">True.intro</span> <span class=\"o\">))</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">True</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">add_true</span> <span class=\"n\">h_new</span>\n  <span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
