    {
        "content": "<p>I think the parentheses around <code>$h:ident</code> make it into a pattern and then Lean gets confused. Without the parentheses, it works:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">macro</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"add_true\"</span> <span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"n\">ident</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">tactic</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">`</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">tactic</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span>\n      <span class=\"k\">have</span> <span class=\"bp\">$</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"n\">ident</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">True</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"n\">True.intro</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">True</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">add_true</span> <span class=\"n\">h_new</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
